{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-paginate","description":"Plug and play pagination plugin for Gatsby","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"kbariotis","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/921760752e826fcf2c6b4d45031ad3aa"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/kbariotis/gatsby-plugin-paginate"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-pagination-plugin\"><a href=\"#gatsby-pagination-plugin\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gatsby Pagination Plugin</h1>\n<p>Just plug and play.</p>\n<p>Check an example of how I am using it on my <a href=\"https://github.com/kbariotis/kostasbariotis.com\">personal website</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm i --save gatsby-plugin-paginate</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"configuration\"><a href=\"#configuration\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Configuration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"plugin\"><a href=\"#plugin\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Plugin</h3>\n<p>In your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module.exports = {\n  plugins: [\n    ...\n    {\n      resolve: `gatsby-plugin-paginate`,\n      options: {\n        sources: [\n          {\n            path: `/page`,\n            pageSize: 5,\n            template: `${__dirname}/src/templates/page.js`,\n            serialize: (results) =&gt; results.allMarkdownRemark.edges,\n            query: `{\n              allMarkdownRemark {\n                edges {\n                  node {\n                    excerpt(pruneLength: 250)\n                    html\n                    id\n                    timeToRead\n                    frontmatter {\n                      date\n                      path\n                      tags\n                      title\n                    }\n                  }\n                }\n              }\n            }`\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n    ...\n  ]\n}</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Configuration Options:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Required</th>\n<th>Purpose</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>path</td>\n<td>false</td>\n<td>The prefix for each page. E.g.: <code class=\"language-text\">/path</code> will become <code class=\"language-text\">/path/1</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">/path/2</code>, etc..</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>template</td>\n<td>true</td>\n<td>Path to the template to be used for each page</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>query</td>\n<td>true</td>\n<td>The GraphQL query to fetch the data to paginate</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>serialize</td>\n<td>false</td>\n<td>If the GraphQL query doesn’t return a list, convert it here</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>pageSize</td>\n<td>false</td>\n<td>The number of items per page</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"template\"><a href=\"#template\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Template</h3>\n<p>The template component will receive a <code class=\"language-text\">pageContext</code> (<code class=\"language-text\">pathContext</code> if you are in Gatsby v1) with the following properties:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Purpose</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>posts</td>\n<td>The collection of items for that page as returned from your GraphQL query</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>page</td>\n<td>The current page number</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>pagesSum</td>\n<td>Total pages number</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>prevPath</td>\n<td>The path to the previous page</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>nextPath</td>\n<td>The path to the next page</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"contribute\"><a href=\"#contribute\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contribute</h2>\n<p>Please open an issue with your specific use case or bug or help me resolve other’s issues. :)</p>","timeToRead":2}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-paginate/","id":"e06cde92-8bb5-571a-a721-05d77b262245"}}